---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SchemaMarkup from '../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro';

const draft = false;
const publishDate = "April 1, 2026";
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "7 min read";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="3 Red Flags to Watch for When Hiring a House Cleaning Service"
  description="Don't get burned by a bad cleaning company. Learn the 3 major red flags to watch for before hiring a local home service in North Alabama."
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="3 Red Flags to Watch for When Hiring a House Cleaning Service"
    description="Don't get burned by a bad cleaning company. Learn the 3 major red flags to watch for before hiring a local home service in North Alabama."
    publishDate={publishDate}
    author={author}
  />
  

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-900 via-gray-800 to-red-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Consumer Protection
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          3 Red Flags When Hiring a<br>
          <span class="text-red-400">Cleaning Service</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>{publishDate}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <article class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">

        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Hiring someone to enter your private space is a massive leap of faith. Unfortunately, not every local service company is built on integrity. Before you hand over your house keys, watch out for these three major red flags.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Red Flag #1: The "Window of Mystery"</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          If a company says, "We'll be there between 1:00 PM and 5:00 PM," they are telling you that their time is more valuable than yours. At The Valley Clean Team, we aren't the cable guy. If we say we'll be there at 9:00 AM, we mean it.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          We use GPS tracking and automated arrival notifications so you are never left wondering where your provider is. You have a busy life-we're here to respect it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Red Flag #2: No Formal Checklist</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          "Clean" means something different to everyone. If a company doesn't have a written, standardized checklist for every room in your home, you are going to get inconsistent results. One week it's great, the next week they missed the master bathroom. 
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          Stability is built on systems. Insist on seeing a checklist from any company you hire. At TVCT, we have a 49-point checklist for every standard clean. Our providers check off every item so you never come home to a half-finished job.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Red Flag #3: No Insurance or Bonding</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          If a cleaner slips on your wet floor or accidentally breaks a $500 vase and they aren't insured, YOU are the one on the hook. "I've been doing this for 20 years" is not a substitute for a valid insurance policy.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          Always ask for proof of insurance and bonding. Any professional company will be happy to provide it. We carry $2 million in liability insurance because your peace of mind is our priority.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Trust is Our Currency</h2>

        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          We believe that a cleaning service should be more than just a transaction-it should be a partnership. By avoiding these red flags, you can ensure that the team in your home is professional, reliable, and respectful of your space.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-600">
          <li><strong>Professionalism:</strong> Clear arrival times and GPS tracking.</li>
          <li><strong>Consistency:</strong> Standardized checklists for every room.</li>
          <li><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong> Fully insured and bonded for your protection.</li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Related Pages Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Services & Service Areas</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a href="/services/house-cleaning" class="block p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-[#FFA985] hover:bg-[#FFA985]/5 transition group">
          <p class="text-[#FFA985] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Service</p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#FFA985] transition">House Cleaning Services →</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/locations/huntsville" class="block p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-[#FFA985] hover:bg-[#FFA985]/5 transition group">
          <p class="text-[#FFA985] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Location</p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#FFA985] transition">Huntsville Cleaning Services →</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/locations/athens" class="block p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-[#FFA985] hover:bg-[#FFA985]/5 transition group">
          <p class="text-[#FFA985] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Location</p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-[#FFA985] transition">Athens AL Cleaning Services →</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready for a Service You Can Trust?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">
        Skip the red flags and book with the professionals. Get your instant quote from The Valley Clean Team today.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-red-600 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-lg">
          Get a Free Quote
        </a>
        <a href="tel:256-826-1100" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gray-900 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors text-lg">
          Call 256-826-1100
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
